headline: Bitcoin touches record high above $93,000 on optimism around Trump's pro-crypto promises
summary: Bitcoin prices pushed to record highs on Wednesday, topping $93,000 and continuing the post-election surge for the world's largest cryptocurrency.

headline: Bitcoin Trades Above $90,000 for First Time
summary: The price of Bitcoin climbed above $90,000 to notch another record, building on a hot streak since Election Day. The largest cryptocurrency by market value surged, recently trading above $92,500, according to CoinDesk data.
